# FSD Boundaries

- Use FSD layers: `app`, `processes`, `pages`, `features`, `entities`, `shared`.
- Keep business logic in `model`; UI components stay in `ui`; helpers in `lib`.
- Do not place business rules inside view components.
- Cross-feature imports must go through stable public API, not deep internal paths.
- Prefer imports via each slice `index.ts` public API.
- New functionality should be added to an existing slice first; create a new slice only when responsibility is truly new.
- If a change breaks layer boundaries, refactor instead of patching around it.
